---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Learn more about my background, experience and interests"
	pubDate={new Date('April 13 2025')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<h2>Hello, I'm Your Name</h2>
	<p>
		I'm a software engineer specializing in front-end development with a passion for creating 
		fast, user-friendly, and accessible web experiences. With over 5 years of experience in the industry,
		I've worked on a variety of projects ranging from simple marketing websites to complex web applications.
	</p>

	<h3>My Approach</h3>
	<p>
		I believe that great software is a combination of clean code, thoughtful design, and focus on the end user.
		I value simplicity, performance, and accessibility in everything I build. My approach involves:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>User-Centered Design:</strong> Putting the needs of users first in every decision</li>
		<li><strong>Performance Optimization:</strong> Creating lightning-fast experiences for all users</li>
		<li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Ensuring products work for everyone, regardless of abilities</li>
		<li><strong>Clean, Maintainable Code:</strong> Writing code that's easy to understand and extend</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Technical Skills</h3>
	<p>
		My core technical skills include:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Languages:</strong> JavaScript (ES6+), TypeScript, HTML5, CSS3</li>
		<li><strong>Frameworks/Libraries:</strong> React, Svelte, Next.js, Astro</li>
		<li><strong>Styling:</strong> Tailwind CSS, CSS-in-JS, SCSS</li>
		<li><strong>Tools:</strong> Git, npm, Webpack, Vite</li>
		<li><strong>Testing:</strong> Jest, React Testing Library, Cypress</li>
		<li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Professional Experience</h3>
	<p>
		In my professional career, I've worked with companies ranging from startups to larger enterprises,
		helping them build better web experiences. My work has included:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Leading front-end development for web applications used by thousands of users daily</li>
		<li>Implementing performance optimizations that significantly improved load times and user engagement</li>
		<li>Collaborating closely with designers and back-end developers to create cohesive products</li>
		<li>Mentoring junior developers and promoting best practices within engineering teams</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Beyond Work</h3>
	<p>
		When I'm not coding, you can find me:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Contributing to open-source projects</li>
		<li>Writing technical blog posts about web development</li>
		<li>Attending and occasionally speaking at tech meetups and conferences</li>
		<li>Hiking, reading, or trying out new coffee shops in my city</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Let's Connect</h3>
	<p>
		I'm always open to discussing new projects, technologies, or opportunities to collaborate. Feel free to reach out
		to me through any of the social links in the footer or via email at your.email@example.com.
	</p>
</Layout>